edu.unc.ils.mrc.hive.api.impl.elmo
Class SKOSSchemeImpl

java.lang.Object
  edu.unc.ils.mrc.hive.api.impl.elmo.SKOSSchemeImpl
All Implemented Interfaces:
SKOSScheme
public class SKOSSchemeImpl
extends java.lang.Object
implements SKOSScheme

This class represents a HIVE vocabulary and associated indexes as described in the HIVE vocabulary property file. Each HIVE vocabulary consists of a Sesame store, Lucene index, and two serialized TreeMaps representing the alphabetic and top-concept indexes.
